Reasoning: The paper deals with the capacity of the consensus version of the Byzantine agreement problem in networks with capacity limited point-to-point links. This involves aspects of distributed computing (cs.DC), network infrastructure (cs.NI), information theory (cs.IT), systems and control (cs.SY), and cryptography and security (cs.CR).
